MBOMBELA &#8211; The SAWS says heavy rain can still be expected in places in the Lowveld today.In Mbombela, 109,6mm rainfall has been recorded over the past 48 hours.In Skukuza, this totalled 127,2mm since the start of the weekend.SAWS said it expected the rainfall to be moderate from Sunday afternoon, and less from Monday onwards.Read more: